Class GlossaryEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • xml.GlossaryEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IGlossaryEntry

    public class GlossaryEntry
extends java.lang.Object
implements IGlossaryEntry
    Class to hold the GlossaryEntry of the requirement analysis. This class provides JAXB support and can be accessed via the IGlossaryEntry Interface. Getter and Setter must be provided to be JAXB conform. It is implemented in the CustomXMLFormat.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    3852430
    See Also:
    IGlossaryEntry, CustomXMLFormat
